# Output Figures

Generated plots are saved here automatically during notebook execution.

## Expected Outputs

1. `01_sample_disks.png` - Sample disk images from dataset
2. `02_training_curves.png` - Training and validation loss
3. `03_reconstruction_comparison.png` - Original vs reconstructed images
4. `04_metric_distributions.png` - MSE and MS-SSIM distributions
5. `05_elbow_curve.png` - Optimal K selection
6. `06_kmeans_umap_clusters.png` - K-Means clusters in UMAP space
7. `07_hdbscan_umap_clusters.png` - HDBSCAN clusters in UMAP space
8. `08_kmeans_pca_clusters.png` - K-Means clusters in PCA space
9. `09_cluster_size_distribution.png` - Cluster size histogram
10. `10_cluster_representatives.png` - Representative images per cluster
11. `11_summary_figure.png` - Comprehensive summary figure
